highlights.text: EM XINH "SAY HI" has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “QUẢ CHÍN QUÁ” is the highest at #50.
“DOORS LIGHT FUNK - SLOWED” by DJ VTTT77, DJ VYZ, and Mc Rd is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #96.
“愛人錯過” by 告五人 has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 194 days straight.
“地球最後的夜晚 - 電視劇《逆愛》片尾主題曲” by 展軒 is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 18 spots at #32.
